(2, '05 / 09 / 2022', 'Logo/6618363770a3f-1712862775.png', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 66, 66);\">My group of company i reeved the best service provider app from Karnataka Media Foundation in the year 2022. Where the company is providing the entire services free of charge.&nbsp;</span></p>', 0, ''),
