(1, 'Start up', 'profile/62dd03587555d-1658651480.jpg', 65, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">Press Club Bangalore is registered as a charitable trust under section 6 of trust act 1860. Besides this we also have licence granted under section 25 of company act, 1956 read with the&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify;\">Government of India,</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;Ministry of Law, Justice and Company Affairs, Notification No. GSR, R288(E) dated 31.05.1991 as 999 Press Club Of India Foundation, Licence number: 102403.</span><br></p>'),
(2, 'Profile', 'profile/62dd03b025446-1658651568.png', 65, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: open_sansregular, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\">Eventually the Press Club of India was founded on December 20, 1957 and incorporated as a company on March 10, &nbsp;1958. It was inaugurated by the then Home Minister Mr G B Pant on February 2, 1959 at the present site. Mr Durga &nbsp;Dass, the then Editor of The Hindustan Times was elected its first president by common consent. Another veteran &nbsp;journalist Mr D R Mankekar became the first secretary general of the Club.</span><br></p>'),
(4, 'Services', 'profile/62dd0466ed5fa-1658651750.jpg', 65, '<p><h3 class=\"entry-title post-title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: open_sansregular, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1em; color: rgb(221, 55, 44); margin: 0.857em 0px; font-size: 30px !important; outline: none !important; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div class=\"vt_moduletable\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"></div></h3></p><h4 style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1em; font-family: open_sansregular, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Conference Room</span></h4><h3 class=\"entry-title post-title\" style=\"line-height: 1em; color: rgb(221, 55, 44); margin-top: 0.857em; margin-bottom: 0.857em; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; vertical-align: baselin