ists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Wingdings;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Company\r\nwill take the Security Deposit of 10,000-00 (ten thousands rupees only) from\r\nevery District Distributor.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Wingdings;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">The\r\nDeposit will be locked for 3 months. Thereafter the candidate can withdraw their\r\ndistribution ship at any moment. After submitting the distribution cancelation\r\napplication the company will cancel their agreement and transfer the\r\ndistribution ship to another candidate name and refund the deposit amount\r\nwithin 30 days. The company will not pay any kind of the interest for their\r\ndeposit.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Wingdings;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">The\r\ncompany will provide 20% of commission and 20% of bonus of their business\r\ntransaction for the candidates as a remediation.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Wingdings;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Company\r\nwill not pay any kind of the fixed salary to the candidates.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Wingdings;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">The\r\ncandidate has to do the minimum target achievement which wi