(19, 'Vijaykumar Ashture', 'Logo/661834391e799-1712862265.png', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 66, 66);\">This is the one of the best local channel OTT platform&nbsp;i found. I am very happy to be a part of this platform in streaming&nbsp;my Kadamba tv in Mymedia. also we are getting the press meet&nbsp;messages and Events information\'s&nbsp;are very helpful for us.</span></p>', 0, 'Chairman, Kadamba News Channel'),
