(22, 'Arun Kumar', 'Logo/6618347c579da-1712862332.png', '<p>This is the very beautiful and one and only application where i found my native place newspapers, magazines and channels. Here i got all my local place newspapers and magazines also my own city tv channel is very helpful to get my native city news and current affairs updates. I really happy with mymedia services.</p>', 0, 'Hardware Engineer, Bengaluru');
